tern-bg-col.jpg?id=470) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1587759396887{margin-top: 20px !important;margin-right: 80px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;background-color: #cbc3bc !important;}\" el_class=\"community\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1587916783490{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h3>WORK OUT<br />\nOR UNWIND</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Break a sweat in our <strong>high-end fitness center</strong> with cycling studio or recharge with yoga.</li>\n<li>Cool off in a sizable <strong>outdoor</strong> <strong>pool</strong> on the mezzanine or catch some shade under an umbrella in the lounge.</li>\n<li>Socialize with neighbors on the expansive <strong>Roof Deck</strong>  complete with <strong>lounge seating, outdoor dining</strong> and <strong>grilling areas.</strong></li>\n<li>Showcase your Iron Chef skills in the <strong>demonstration kitchen</strong>.</li>\n<li>Take in the city views from<strong> two lush terraces</strong> with fire pits.</li>\n<li>Unwind in <strong>environmentally friendly public and private spaces</strong> with outdoor seating.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1587916643684{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h3>service your<br />\nevery need</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Enjoy a <strong>24-7 concierge, free Wifi</strong> in shared spaces and <strong>Dryy garment care service</strong> in the building.</li>\n<li>Stock up at the ground-floor neighborhood <strong>grocery store</strong>.</li>\n<li><strong>Take your dog for a walk</strong> in the plaza and keep them looking good with our <strong>pet-care services</strong>.</li>\n<li